From: PDFViewer Build <build@pdfviewer.local>
Subject: [PATCH 3/5] Disable Skia dependency for emscripten builds

Skia graphics library doesn't compile well for WASM and isn't needed
for PDFium's core PDF rendering functionality.

---
 BUILD.gn | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/BUILD.gn b/BUILD.gn
--- a/BUILD.gn
+++ b/BUILD.gn
@@ -1,5 +1,5 @@
-  if (defined(checkout_skia) && checkout_skia && !is_android) {
+  # Patched: Disabled skia for emscripten/wasm builds
+  if (defined(checkout_skia) && checkout_skia && !is_android && target_os != "emscripten") {
     deps += [ "//skia" ]
   }
